        <div xml:id="TK1051">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>irakka irattakkārk kāṇiṟ karappiṉ </l>
<l>avarpaḻi tampaḻi yaṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>If you meet with those that may be begged of, you may beg; (but) if they withhold (their gift) it is their blame and not yours.</l>
            </lg>
